
?ExprX $\= ?ExprY

   ExprX is not equal to ExprY.

Arguments
   ExprX               Arithmetic expression
   ExprY               Arithmetic expression

Type
   library(ic)

Description

   Constrains ExprX and ExprY to not be equal.  Alternate form of
   ic:(ExprX =\= ExprY).
